commit.message:
Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/partyrico/icebox
icebox.db is different since new recipes have been added
Added an iterative process to allrecipes so that scrapper doesn't have to run recursively (ending when it hits a recursive limit)

Stores images of each crop

the stored images can be used to improve the model used for future readings.
Use Clarifai and opencv to read text from an image
Added app.wsgi for use in apache

Add files via upload

Uses Clarifai and opencv to cut an image into individual letters, and then read the sub-images with the Clarifai API
Modified .gitignore to stop moving db around

Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/partyrico/icebox
Just fixing db since my db has more recipes!
Changes made to index.tpl and main.css
Fixed the way instructions and ingredients are displayed by removing the unicode icon at beginning of text
Added a lot of recipes, now about 4,500
